        <hl1>Word's Not Perfect</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>As a longtime WordPerfect user, I never use Microsoft Word even though it takes up space on the hard drive. I recently purchased a Gateway laptop in which Microsoft Word was bundled. I was not, however, able to purchase WordPerfect as an option through Gateway.</p>
        <p>RODELLE WEINTRAUB  State College, Pa.</p>
      </block>
